35 Puppy Linux JWM/Rox combo
Update your system first
sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade

Install JWM (Joe’s Window Manager)
sudo apt install jwm

Install ROX-Filer
sudo apt install rox-filer

Bind ROX to the desktop
Create or edit your .xinitrc or session startup file:
rox --pinboard=Default &
exec jwm

Optional: Add Puppy-like session
You can create a custom .desktop entry under /usr/share/xsessions/ called jwm-rox.desktop:
[Desktop Entry]
Name=JWM + ROX
Comment=Puppy Linux style session
Exec=rox --pinboard=Default & jwm
Type=Application

