40 River
Install Dependencies
sudo apt install build-essential meson ninja-build \
  pkg-config libwayland-dev libxkbcommon-dev \
  libwlroots-dev libdrm-dev libpixman-1-dev \
  libinput-dev libudev-dev

Clone the River Repository
git clone https://github.com/riverwm/river.git
cd river

Build with Meson/Ninja
meson setup build
ninja -C build
sudo ninja -C build install

Configure River
Create a startup script:
mkdir -p ~/.config/river
nano ~/.config/river/init

Example init file:
#!/bin/sh
riverctl map normal Super Return spawn foot
riverctl map normal Super Q close
riverctl map normal Super D spawn wofi --show drun
rivertile -view-padding 5 -outer-padding 5 &

Make it executable:
chmod +x ~/.config/river/init

Start River
river

